<div id="volks">
    <h3>1. Volkswagen</h3>
    <p style="width:60%">
        It was claimed that the cars being sold by Volkswagen were fitted with devices that appears
        to put the vehicle under a sort of safety mode which could detect when they were being tested,
        causing the engine to run below normal power and performance. After the engines were switched
        out of the test mode, it was shown that the engines emitted nitrogen oxide pollutants up to
        40 times above what is allowed in the US.
    </p>
